Package: steward-node
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: Hardrails <support@hardrails.dev>
Depends: passwd, systemd, util-linux
Homepage: https://github.com/hardrails/steward
Description: Sovereign Steward agent execution node
 Installs the Steward lifecycle supervisor and Docker/gVisor executor as separate,
 hardened systemd services. Installation is offline and noninteractive; services
 remain disabled until the operator provisions trust material and runs preflight.
